# Server
PORT=3001
FRONTEND_ORIGIN=http://127.0.0.1:5173

# ── Apple Music ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Required for the /apple-music/token endpoint that MusicKit JS SDK needs.
#
# How to get these values:
# 1. Sign in to https://developer.apple.com/account
# 2. Certificates, Identifiers & Profiles → Keys → Create a new MusicKit key
# 3. Download the AuthKey_XXXXXXXXXX.p8 file (keep it safe — can only download once)
# 4. Your Team ID is shown in the top-right corner of the developer portal
# 5. The Key ID is the 10-character code in the filename and in the portal
#
# In this file paste the full contents of the .p8 file on ONE line,
# replacing every real newline with the two characters \n
# Example: -----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----\nMIGHAgEAMBMGByq...\n-----END PRIVATE KEY-----
APPLE_TEAM_ID=YOUR_10_CHAR_TEAM_ID
APPLE_KEY_ID=YOUR_10_CHAR_KEY_ID
APPLE_PRIVATE_KEY=-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----\nYOUR_KEY_CONTENTS_HERE\n-----END PRIVATE KEY-----
